<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I think it is helpful to start with the big pi=
cture. Elon Musk is the richest person in the world, and, like many other r=
ich people, he has some unusual and expensive hobbies. One of his hobbies i=
s that he sometimes likes to=C2=A0pretend=C2=A0that he will acquire public =
companies.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: =
#000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border=
-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-co=
lor: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0He seems to find this fun, and why not?=C2=A0When he pretends tha=
t he=E2=80=99ll buy a public company, it creates a big drama with him at th=
e center of it. He gets to boss people around, mobilize legions of bankers =
and lawyers and financing sources and random hangers-on<a class=3D"footnote=
-index" href=3D"#footnote-2" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; d=
isplay: inline-block;">
<span>[2]</span>
</a>=C2=A0hoping to get the deal done, and then when he gets bored he can t=
ell all those people to go home. =E2=80=9CHaha got you,=E2=80=9D he can say=
, and they can all have a good laugh, or he can anyway.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is an expensive hobby! When Musk=C2=A0<a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28323083.276576/aHR0c=
HM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDgtMTMvZnVuZGlu=
Zy1mb3ItZWxvbi1tdXNrLXMtdGVzbGEtYnV5b3V0LXdhc24tdC1zby1zZWN1cmU_Y21waWQ9QkJ=
EMDcwOTIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZX=
ImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIwNzA5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319=
a23cB811099df/email" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">pretended</a>=C2=A0in 2018=C2=A0that he was g=
oing to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28323083.2=
76576/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDgtM=
DgvZWxvbi1tdXNrLWhhcy1zb21lLWZ1bi13aXRoLXRlc2xhP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA3MDkyMl9NT05F=
WVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI=
yMDcwOSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0dd644a1/e=
mail" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" styl=
e=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width:=
 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;"> take Tesla Inc. private</a>, he had to pay the US Securities=
 and Exchange Commission=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusines=
s.com/click/28323083.276576/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2F=
ydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMTAtMDEvdGVzbGEtd2lsbC10cnktdG8tYmUtbW9yZS1ub3JtYWw_Y21waW=
Q9QkJEMDcwOTIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZ=
XR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIwNzA5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b852=
4a319a23cB84fdea62/email" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" ta=
rget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; =
border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style=
: solid; background-color: #ccc;">a $20 million fine</a>=C2=A0and stop bein=
g the chairman of Tesla=E2=80=99s board. You=E2=80=99re not really supposed=
 to go around pretending that you will buy a public company; the SEC someti=
mes considers that securities fraud. But Musk is very rich and he can easil=
y afford to pay $20 million for his little joke. His appetite for pretendin=
g to buy public companies was, apparently, undiminished.</p>
