e: solid; background-color: #ccc;">gave himself an excuse</a> to sell a bun=
ch of Tesla stock near the highs. He=C2=A0maybe <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28323083.276576/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhldmVyZ2UuY=
29tLzIwMjIvNS8yLzIzMDU0MTkzL3R3aXR0ZXItZWRpdC1idXR0b24taG93LWl0LXdvcmtzLWxv=
b2tzLWxpa2U/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBc4c20a3e/email" itemprop=3D"StoryLink"=
 itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">got an edit bu=
tton too</a>? Maybe that=E2=80=99s worth a billion dollars to him?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I tell you what though. <em>I </em>have learne=
d my lesson. The next time Elon Musk announces that he is going to buy a pu=
blic company =E2=80=94=C2=A0and he will=C2=A0do it again! =E2=80=94=C2=A0I =
will know not to believe him. I will definitely know not to write about it.=
</p>
